Kredietbank opens Philippines unit . Kredietbank NV , Belgium ' s fourth largest bank , said on Friday it had set up an off - shore banking unit in the Philippines . Kredietbank NV Manila will principally finance trade between southeast Asia and the rest of the world and also Asian Development Bank ( ADB ) projects , Kredietbank said in a statement . The ADB is based in Manila . Kredietbank said it recently opened a representative office in Jakarta , Indonesia , to add to its existing Asian operations in Hong Kong , Singapore , Taipei , Bangkok and Shanghai . - - Brussels Newsroom + 32 2 287 6810 , Fax + 32 2 230 7710 
